<br>
Your pet seems to die very quickly, simply because it is not very strong <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  At level 4 you could/should try getting a yellow or at least even con pet, it will help a lot.<br>
<br>
Also try giving pet (if you can afford it) a HIGH damage weapon, like rusty 2h sword or scyte, as this will make him hit MUCH harder, this works for pets up to and including level 12.<br>
<br>
As for solo or group, I found that a small group, or a partner was the best for safety AND good exp.<br>
